OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FVariable cloud and a few
OL,6,Fshowers to start. Showers will become
OL,7,Fmore frequent from late morning
OL,8,Fonwards, and some of these will be
OL,9,Fheavy and perhaps thundery at times.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FSome showers at first but
OL,12,Fthese dying out through the evening.
OL,13,FStaying mostly dry overnight and
OL,14,Flargely cloudy, but a few clear spells
OL,15,Fin places.
OL,16,
OL,17,CSunday:FCloudy in the morning with a
OL,18,Ffew showers. Again showers becoming
OL,19,Fmore frequent from late morning
OL,20,Fonwards, heavy and perhaps thundery at
OL,21,Ftimes.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
